{"tid":1569063,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"好驚，今日淘大有懷疑休班克警唔帶委任證執法","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:58:40.000Z","uid":174953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b03c08ad7f152597d748a6beb83e753fa28b96d","tid":1569063,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"我點知佢係唔係真？點知佢唔係假扮？咁如果有人帶住伸縮警棍或手扣，就代表佢係休班克警？<br />\n<br />\n咁佢咪可以執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家我睇新聞啲休班克警都唔洗帶委任證執法<br />\n<br />\n咁之後如果有人咁做咪好危險，周街都係克警都可以隨時捉人，咁如果一個唔小心捉我依啲撐警藍絲我咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要比人仆幾棍，又要比人搭住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時仇都無得報<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時我唔知信唔信條友真係休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果我懷疑佢係假，點知原來真，郁手打佢咪變咗襲警<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係一個撐警藍絲好守法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家淘寶仲要好易買到警棍，到時全民休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我身為一個撐警藍絲睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.14&amp;id=557407118573&amp;item_id=557407118573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fspm%3Da21wu.11154615-hk.list.14%26id%3D557407118573%26item_id%3D557407118573&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=c33bffe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.14&amp;id=557407118573&amp;item_id=557407118573</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/701147650/TB2Fb.shVXXXXXHXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!701147650.jpg_760x760q75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.